-chapter padding-top-and-bottom padding-bottom-smaller custom-padding-regul=
ar"><div class=3D"container"><div class=3D"page-content"><h1>An easy guide =
to finding your ideal bike size</h1><div class=3D"text regular-text"><p>Is =
it just us, or are bikes more popular than ever? They come in so many shape=
s, sizes, and colors. Some come with cool accessories that support all kind=
s of riders =E2=80=93 super parents with kids tagging along in the back, or=
 front baskets for pampered pets! Loads of people have switched to cycling =
as a smart way to live more mindfully - and save costs on fuel. If this is =
your first time picking a bike or maybe you haven=E2=80=99t ridden one in a=
 long time =E2=80=93 our handy guide to finding the right bike size will he=
lp!</p><p>Choosing a bike that=E2=80=99s just right for you is like picking=
 the perfect pair of jeans =E2=80=93 lots to be considered but so worth it =
in the long run. This article has practical tips to help you pick the right=
 bike size and make your bike-picking journey hassle-free. All you=E2=80=99=
ll need is a measuring tape to get started.</p></div></div></div></div><div=
 id=3D"element-27843" class=3D"content-wrapper content-wrapper-image paddin=
g-top-none padding-bottom-smaller"><div class=3D"container text-center"><pi=
cture><source media=3D"(max-width: 799px)" srcset=3D"https://images2.giant-=
bicycles.com/b_none%2Cc_pad%2Cq_80/qyih2jtw5t8put9spavs/800_1219_1.jpg"><so=
urce media=3D"(min-width: 800px)" srcset=3D"https://images2.giant-bicycles.=
com/b_none%2Cc_pad%2Cq_80/a6n5udrkihmz4u0xovb9/Banner_1140_1216_1.jpg"><img=
 src=3D"https://images2.giant-bicycles.com/b_none%2Cc_pad%2Cq_80/a6n5udrkih=
mz4u0xovb9/Banner_1140_1216_1.jpg" alt=3D"TBD" class=3D"img-responsive" sty=
le=3D"margin:0 auto"> </picture></div></div><div id=3D"element-27844" class=
=3D"content-wrapper-page-element content-wrapper-page-element-chapter paddi=
ng-top-none custom-padding-regular"><div class=3D"container"><div class=3D"=
page-content"><h2>Top tip: Decide what type of bike you want before figurin=
g out the perfect bike size for you</h2><div class=3D"text regular-text"><p=
>Your ideal bike size depends on the type of bike you want, plus your heigh=
t and physical strength. Understandably commuter bikes are very different t=
o mountain bikes, which are also very different to cargo bikes. Aside from =
the obvious large versus small size difference, these bikes come in differe=
nt shapes and are fitted with different accessories and parts because they=
=E2=80=99re designed for different lifestyles.</p><p>For example, a mountai=
n bike is designed for someone who loves the great outdoors and isn=E2=80=
=99t afraid of getting dirty. The tires are wider and larger; the bike fram=
e and other parts are thicker and heavier; and it=E2=80=99ll probably have =
a water bottle cage (yes, not all bikes have one!). All these features help=
 the rider conquer tough terrains.</p><p>At momentum we have a unique bike =
size chart for all our bikes, whether you=E2=80=99re looking at the <a href=
=3D"https://www.momentum-biking.com/PakYak" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noopen=
er">PakYak E+ cargo e-bike</a>, the sturdy Vida Low-Step leisure bike or ou=
r newest <a href=3D"https://www.momentum-biking.com/Voya" target=3D"_blank"=
 rel=3D"noopener">Voya E+ commuter e-bike</a>. To find out more <a href=3D"=
